                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
                <div class="media block-6 services mb-md-0 mb-4">
                    <div class="icon bg-color-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-2">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-fast" style="font-size: 30px; color: white;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="heading">Hỗ trợ</h3>
                        <span>Giao hàng tận nơi</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="ftco-section ftco-category ftco-no-pt" style="margin-top: 0px;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-last align-items-stretch d-flex">
                        <div class="category-wrap-2 ftco-animate img align-self-stretch d-flex" style="background-image: url('/img/thiết kế chưa có tên (1).png');">
                            <div class="text text-center">
                                <h2 style="color: #dd781a !important">Đồ lưu niệm</h2>
                                <p>Hãy lựa chọn những món quà cho gia đình</p>
                                <p><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home" style="background:#dd781a !important; 
                                                     border: none; 
                                                     border-radius: 2px;
                                                     color: white; 
                                                     padding:5px 20px;">Cửa hàng</a></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="category-wrap ftco-animate img mb-4 d-flex align-items-end" style="background-image: url('/img/382596221_3570980819840954_4187970744932620810_n.jpg');">
                        </div>
                        <div class="category-wrap ftco-animate img d-flex align-items-end" style="background-image: url('/img/386107835_3577064765899226_4485664415835025727_n.jpg');">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="category-wrap ftco-animate img mb-4 d-flex align-items-end" style="background-image: url('/img/393313674_3582076468731389_87825007127327399_n.jpg');">
                </div>
                <div class="category-wrap ftco-animate img d-flex align-items-end" style="background-image: url('/img/399021754_3593123784293324_7077732482559538422_n.jpg');">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
@if (TempData["Message"] != null)
{
    <div class="alert__thongbao">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-check" style="color: #ffffff;"></i>
        @TempData["Message"]
    </div>
}
<section class="ftco-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center mb-3 pb-3">
            <div class="col-md-12 heading-section text-center ftco-animate">
                <span class="subheading" style="color: #dd781a !important;">Sản phẩm</span>
                <h2 class="mb-4">Các sản phẩm nổi bật</h2>
                <p>Hãy tới cửa hàng để có nhiều lựa chọn hơn nhé!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            @{
                foreach (var item in ViewBag.ListProduct)
                {
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 ftco-animate contaner__content--trangchu">
                        <div class="product">
                            <a style="height: 240px;" class="img-prod">
                                <img class="img-fluid" src="@Url.Action("GetImage", "SanPham", new { id = @item.Id})" alt="Colorlib Template">
                            </a>
                            <div class="text py-3 pb-4 px-3 text-center">
                                <h3><a>@item.Ten</a></h3>
                                <h3 style="font-size:13px; height: 35px;"><a class="product__trang--thai">@item.CuaHang.Ten</a></h3>
                                <div class="d-flex">
                                    <div class="pricing">
                                        <p class="price"><span class="price-sale">@item.Gia.ToString("C3")</span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bottom-area d-flex px-3">
                                    <div class="m-auto d-flex">
                                        <a asp-action="Product" asp-controller="Home" asp-route-id="@item.Id" class="add-to-cart d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center text-center">
                                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-list"></i></span>
                                        </a>
                                        <a href="/GioHang/AddToGioHang?sanPhamId=@item.Id" class="buy-now d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mx-1">
                                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i></span>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            }
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="ftco-section img" style="background: url(/img/z4948448986151_c1d081626f73786c95fd363e3d17c8fa.jpg) no-repeat fixed !important; padding:2rem 0; ">
    <div class="container d-flex" style="justify-content:center; gap: 5rem;">
        <div class="row" style="width:50%">
            <img style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; border-radius:2px;" src="@Url.Action("GetImage", "SanPham", new { id = @ViewBag.LastProduct.Id})" />
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center" style="width:100%;">
            <div class="col-md-6 heading-section ftco-animate deal-of-the-day ftco-animate" style="width:50%; margin-top:2rem;">
                <span class="subheading" style="color: #dd781a;">Sản phẩm mới nhất</span>
                <h2 class="mb-4" style="width:100%; font-size:25px;">@ViewBag.LastProduct.Ten</h2>

                <span><a style="color: #1C65A1; font-size: 18px;">@ViewBag.LastProduct.CuaHang.Ten</a></span> <br />

                <span><a style="color: black; font-size: 14px;">@ViewBag.LastProduct.CuaHang.DiaChi</a></span>

                <h3><a style="color: black; font-size: 18px;">Giá bán</a></h3>
                <span class="price" style="font-size:27px; color: #e83939; font-weight:600;">@ViewBag.LastProduct.Gia.ToString("C3")</span>
                <p><a asp-action="Product" asp-controller="Home" asp-route-id="@ViewBag.LastProduct.Id" style="color:#1a51dd;">Chi tiết <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="ftco-section testimony-section" style="background: white;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center pb-3">
            <div class="col-md-7 heading-section ftco-animate text-center">
                <span class="subheading" style="color: #dd781a;">Bình luận</span>
                <h2 class="mb-4">Khách hàng hài lòng nói gì về chúng tôi ?</h2>
                <p>Một số bình luận của khách hàng</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row ftco-animate">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="carousel-testimony owl-carousel">
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="testimony-wrap p-4 pb-5">
                            <div class="user-img mb-5" style="background-image: url('/img/person_1.jpg')">
                                <span class="quote d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <i class="icon-quote-left"></i>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text text-center">
                                <p class="mb-5 pl-4 line">Shop bán giá cả rất hợp lý, chủ shop vui tính , giao hàng nhanh với dịch vụ giao hàng tận giường, đảm bảo hàng hoá tới tận tay khách hàng không có vấn đề gì 10 điểm không nhưng!</p>
                                <p class="name">Sỹ Lê</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="testimony-wrap p-4 pb-5">
                            <div class="user-img mb-5" style="background-image: url(images/person_2.jpg)">
                                <span class="quote d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <i class="icon-quote-left"></i>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text text-center">
                                <p class="mb-5 pl-4 line">Shop gói hàng rất kĩ đảm bảo hàng hoá không bị ảnh hưởng, giao tận tay khách hàng, đảm bảo sản phẩm tới đã nhận được hàng kiểm hàng mới thanh toán dịch vụ tốt 10 điểm</p>
                                <p class="name">Phi Long</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="testimony-wrap p-4 pb-5">
                            <div class="user-img mb-5" style="background-image: url(images/person_3.jpg)">
                                <span class="quote d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <i class="icon-quote-left"></i>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text text-center">
                                <p class="mb-5 pl-4 line">Shop có tâm nhất hệ mặt trời, quá tuyệt vời</p>
                                <p class="name">Tuấn</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

